==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zirconium
<hw>Zir*co"ni*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A rare element of the carbon-silicon group,
intermediate between the metals and nonmetals, obtained from the mineral
zircon as a dark sooty powder, or as a gray metallic crystalline
substance. Symbol Zr. Atomic weight, 90.4.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

